title: Prince e-Sports Holding Tryouts
body:
Prince e-Sports is currently holding open tryouts for our OOL Main Roster.

We would like you to be D2+ and have past competitive experience. To attract a team of like-minded individuals, there will be financial incentives available for players. We are looking to build a strong team whose goal is to compete at the top of OOL.

We are also looking for a talented coach for this team. If you have past experience and are interested in coaching a team to OOL success, this is a great opportunity for you.

Tryouts will take place on Thursday and Saturday this week. More information can be provided upon request.

If interested, you can add me, Torpid or i am sleepy in-client, or go to our website and apply there.

Thanks for reading.

http://www.princeesports.com
